{
  "script_id": "green-theorem",
  "voice": "zh-CN-YunxiNeural",
  "voice_key": "yunxi",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "green-theorem",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/green-theorem/yunxi/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.5,
      "size": 40032,
      "text": "想象平面上有一片水流, 每一点都有自己的流速和方向, 这就是一个向量场。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "green-theorem",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/green-theorem/yunxi/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.93,
      "size": 30816,
      "text": "现在我们画一条封闭的曲线, 让它围住一小块区域。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "green-theorem",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/green-theorem/yunxi/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.3,
      "size": 36864,
      "text": "格林公式告诉我们, 沿这条边界绕一圈的总效果, 只由区域内部决定。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "green-theorem",
      "section_id": "curl",
      "line_id": "curl-1",
      "filename": "curl-curl-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/green-theorem/yunxi/curl-curl-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.21,
      "size": 35280,
      "text": "在场里的每一点, 我们都能问: 这里的水流有没有打转的趋势。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "green-theorem",
      "section_id": "curl",
      "line_id": "curl-2",
      "filename": "curl-curl-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/green-theorem/yunxi/curl-curl-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.6,
      "size": 41616,
      "text": "这个打转的强度, 就是旋度, 等于 Q 对 x 的偏导数, 减去 P 对 y 的偏导数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "green-theorem",
      "section_id": "curl",
      "line_id": "curl-3",
      "filename": "curl-curl-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/green-theorem/yunxi/curl-curl-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.7,
      "size": 43200,
      "text": "旋度为正表示逆时针旋转, 为负表示顺时针, 为零则说明这里不打转。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "green-theorem",
      "section_id": "theorem",
      "line_id": "thm-2",
      "filename": "theorem-thm-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/green-theorem/yunxi/theorem-thm-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.01,
      "size": 32112,
      "text": "左边是边界上的环量, 右边是内部所有微小旋转的总和。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "green-theorem",
      "section_id": "theorem",
      "line_id": "thm-3",
      "filename": "theorem-thm-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/green-theorem/yunxi/theorem-thm-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.42,
      "size": 38736,
      "text": "无数个小旋转在内部彼此抵消, 只剩下最外圈的边界留下痕迹。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "green-theorem",
      "section_id": "area",
      "line_id": "area-1",
      "filename": "area-area-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/green-theorem/yunxi/area-area-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.12,
      "size": 33984,
      "text": "选一个旋度恒为一的场, 二重积分就正好等于区域的面积。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "green-theorem",
      "section_id": "area",
      "line_id": "area-2",
      "filename": "area-area-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/green-theorem/yunxi/area-area-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.58,
      "size": 41328,
      "text": "于是只要沿着边界走一圈做线积分, 就能算出里面的面积, 完全不用碰内部。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "green-theorem",
      "section_id": "area",
      "line_id": "area-3",
      "filename": "area-area-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/green-theorem/yunxi/area-area-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.35,
      "size": 37584,
      "text": "测量仪器求积仪, 正是靠这个原理, 描一圈轮廓就读出面积。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "green-theorem",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/green-theorem/yunxi/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.39,
      "size": 38304,
      "text": "切换不同的向量场, 观察边界环量和内部旋度如何一一对应。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "green-theorem",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/green-theorem/yunxi/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.29,
      "size": 36720,
      "text": "试试保守场, 旋度处处为零, 绕一圈的线积分也恰好是零。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "green-theorem",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/green-theorem/yunxi/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.94,
      "size": 31104,
      "text": "格林公式把边界的线积分, 换成了区域的二重积分。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "green-theorem",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/green-theorem/yunxi/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.27,
      "size": 36288,
      "text": "它是微积分基本定理在平面上的推广, 也是斯托克斯定理的雏形。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "green-theorem",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/green-theorem/yunxi/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.73,
      "size": 27648,
      "text": "边界与内部在这里紧紧相连, 我们下次再见。"
    }
  ],
  "total_duration": 36.34,
  "total_size": 581616
}